        <h2 class="twoLines">VPS Hosting</h2>
        <p>Vivanta Technologies is an ideal place for numerous Hosting assistance service provider. We are a reliable VPS Hosting assistance service provider Bangalore which provides assistance for various internet companies. Virtual Private Server (VPS) hosting has a wide range of hosting options for your site which gives you a better performance. The VPS Hosting is the next level of performance that can be used for shared hosting to give you more functionality and improved performance. </p>
<p>VPS hosting assistance service provider companies guide you with the entire process in providing features, applications and exciting plans for virtual servers.</p>
  <h2 class="twoLines">What is a Virtual Private Server (VPS)?</h2>      
<p>It is a virtual machine that runs its own copy of the operating system and customers have superuser-level access to that operating system (Windows, Linux, Ubuntu, etc.,) instance, so can install almost any software that runs on that OS. A virtual server splits a physical server into multiple virtual servers. Each server is protected with the reserved amount of CPU and RAM resources. VPS bridges the gap between shared web hosting services and dedicated hosting services, giving a full-fledge control from other customers.</p>
<br>
<h3 class="twoLines">Usage:</h3>
<p>VPS Hosting mainly benefits for businesses as well as users who are experiencing a rapid growth, high website traffic or running complex applications. The performance can drive the combination of Hardware, number of VPS hosted on that server and Virtualization Technology. For instance; you can use simultaneous operating systems without needing to restart your PC/Laptop.</p>
<h3 class="twoLines">Vivanta Technologies VPS Hosting Assistance</h3>
<ul class="normal dot"><li>Ability to customize configurations and installations.</li>
<li>It is flexible and easy to set up the VPS hosting services.</li>
<li>Provides more security with better performance.</li>
<li>Dedicate mail server.</li>
<li>Benefited for the users running complicated applications.</li>
<li>Well-suited for sites experiencing high traffic.</li>
<li>Exciting Hosting Plan features.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="twoLines">Benefits of VPS Hosting:</h2>
<br>
<h3 class="twoLines">Flexibility and Reliability</h3>
<p>VPS Hosting has a better flexibility and reliability, scaling up the level of performance with virtual servers using its own CPU and RAM resources. This facilitates to install either Windows or Linux on your server.</p>
<h3 class="twoLines">Affordable Costs</h3>
<p>VPS hosting services plans are economical which is best suited for small and medium size businesses. With this plan, you will get more features and options based with high performance.</p>
<h3 class="twoLines">Dedicated Resources</h3>
<p>VPS hosting services allow you to have own server and give access to dedicated resources such as; CPU, RAM and more storage capacity.  This will allow you to have control over your VPS with full root access to your virtual server and has the ability to reboot remotely.</p>
<p>Vivanta Technologies is a dedicated VPS hosting assistance provider with different plan options and supported features for server hosting. Our technical experts guide you with the entire process of VPS hosting server backed with guarantee policy and scalability.</p>
